public class AnalyzingSailConnection
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.openrdf.sail.SailConnection, AnalyzingConnection

Analyzer for Sail connections. Monitors connections and calls to getStatements + evaluate. Note: hasStatements from RepositoryConnection is included in this!
